{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-022","title":"Sentence 22","sectionId":"sentences-021","sectionTitle":"Sentence 21-30","pageStart":158,"pageEnd":163,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":48,"duplicateEntryCount":7,"pages":[{"number":158,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 22"},{"type":"text","text":"Since wind-pollinated flowers have no need to attract insects or other"},{"type":"text","text":"animals, they have dispensed with bright petals, nectar, and scent."},{"type":"text","text":"由于靠风传播授粉的花不需要吸引昆虫或其他动物，所以它们"},{"type":"text","text":"不再需要色彩鲜艳的花瓣、花蜜和气味。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是“They have dispensed with petals, nectar, and scent”，"},{"type":"text","text":"其中dispense with是固定搭配，意为“不再需要”。句首的since引导一个"},{"type":"text","text":"原因状语从句。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"wind-pollinated /ˈwɪndˈpɑləˌneɪtɪd/ a. 靠风传播授粉的","headword":"wind-pollinated"},{"type":"entry","text":"attract /əˈtrækt/ vt. 吸引，引起（注意等）","headword":"attract"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 at（加强）+tract（拉）→不断拉（眼球）→吸引"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 be attracted to sth. 被…所吸引"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 lure vt. 吸引，诱惑"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 attractive a. 吸引人的"},{"type":"text","text":"attraction n. 吸引，诱惑"},{"type":"text","text":"attractant n. 引诱物"},{"type":"entry","text":"dispense /dɪˈspens/ vt. 分发；豁免","headword":"dispense"}]},{"number":159,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 dis（分开）+pens（花费）+e→把花费分开→分配"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 dispense with sb./sth. 不再需要；摒弃"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 dispensable a. 不必要的"},{"type":"text","text":"dispensation n. 分配；实施"},{"type":"entry","text":"petal /ˈpetl/ n. 花瓣","headword":"petal"},{"type":"entry","text":"nectar /ˈnektər/ n. 花蜜；琼浆玉液","headword":"nectar"},{"type":"entry","text":"scent /sent/ n. 香气；气味","headword":"scent"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 fragrance n. 香味"},{"type":"text","text":"odor n. 气味"},{"type":"text","text":"smell n. 气味"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“花、草”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"blossom /ˈblɑːsəm/ n. 花；开花","headword":"blossom"},{"type":"entry","text":"bouquet /buˈkeɪ/ n. 花束","headword":"bouquet"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 banquet n. 宴会，盛宴"},{"type":"entry","text":"bud /bʌd/ n. 芽，蓓蕾","headword":"bud"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 泥土（mud）中发出的芽（bud）"},{"type":"entry","text":"chlorophyll /ˈklɔːrəfɪl/ n. 叶绿素","headword":"chlorophyll"},{"type":"entry","text":"coronary /ˈkɔːrəneri/ a. 花冠的","headword":"coronary"}]},{"number":160,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"exuberant /ɪɡˈzuːbərənt/ a. 繁茂的","headword":"exuberant"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ex（加强）+uber（果实）+ant（…的）→全都是果实的→繁"},{"type":"text","text":"茂的"},{"type":"entry","text":"floral /ˈflɔːrəl/ a. 花的；植物群的","headword":"floral"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 flor（花）+al（…的）→花的"},{"type":"entry","text":"floriculture /ˈflɔrɪˌkʌltʃər/ n. 花卉栽培","headword":"floriculture"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 flori（花）+cult（耕种）+ure→花草栽培"},{"type":"entry","text":"foliage /ˈfoʊliɪdʒ/ n. （植物的）叶","headword":"foliage"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 foli（树叶）+age（表总称）→叶"}]},{"number":161,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"grassy /ˈɡræsi/ a. 长满草的","headword":"grassy"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 grassy plain 草原"},{"type":"entry","text":"herb /ɜːrb/ n. 草本植物","headword":"herb"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 herbicide n. 除草剂"},{"type":"text","text":"herbivore n. 草食动物"},{"type":"entry","text":"photosynthesis /ˌfoʊtoʊˈsɪnθəsɪs/ n. 光合作用","headword":"photosynthesis"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 photo（光）+synthesis（合成）→光合作用"},{"type":"entry","text":"pistil /ˈpɪstɪl/ n. 雌蕊","headword":"pistil"},{"type":"entry","text":"pollen /ˈpɑːlən/ n. 花粉","headword":"pollen"},{"type":"entry","text":"pollinate /ˈpɑːləneɪt/ vt. 给…授粉","headword":"pollinate"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 pollination n. 授粉"},{"type":"text","text":"pollinator n. 传粉媒介，传粉昆虫"},{"type":"entry","text":"seed /siːd/ n. 种子","headword":"seed"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 seed player 种子选手"},{"type":"entry","text":"sprayer /ˈspreɪər/ n. 喷雾