:"同根 fascination n. 迷恋"},{"type":"text","text":"fascinating a. 吸引人的"},{"type":"entry","text":"glamorous /ˈɡlæmərəs/ a. 富有魅力的，迷人的","headword":"glamorous"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 来自glamor（n. 魅力）"},{"type":"entry","text":"grip /ɡrɪp/ v./n. 紧抓；吸引住…的注意力（或想象力等）","headword":"grip"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 和trip（n. 旅行）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"intriguing /ɪnˈtriːɡɪŋ/ a. 引起兴趣（或好奇心）的，吸引人的","headword":"intriguing"},{"type":"entry","text":"inviting /ɪnˈvaɪtɪŋ/ a. 动人的，诱人的","headword":"inviting"},{"type":"entry","text":"magnet /ˈmæɡnət/ n. 磁铁；有吸引力的人（或事物）","headword":"magnet"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 magnetism n. 磁力"},{"type":"text","text":"magnetize vt. 磁化"},{"type":"entry","text":"mesmerize /ˈmezməraɪz/ vt. 施催眠术；使入迷","headword":"mesmerize"},{"type":"entry","text":"tempt /tempt/ vt. 诱使；引起…的兴趣","headword":"tempt"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 temptation n. 诱惑物"},{"type":"text","text":"tempting a. 吸引人的"}]}]}